Telkom has received a new number range, according to an email sent to business partners which has been seen by MyBroadband. The email stated that the range was allocated to Telkom this month and is situated within the 068 number group. The new range spans 068 numbers from 000 0000 to 599 9999. This results in a total of six million new numbers available to Telkom Mobile. Following the allocation of this 068 number range, Telkom now has access to the 061, 065, 067, 068, and 081 number ranges. To learn more about which ranges are operated by which mobile networks and what they mean, read this breakdown of number range allocations.